{"tid":1301316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【復活大白象】廣東省：「壽終正寢」的港深西部快軌將重新啟動","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:56:19.000Z","uid":37554,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6423fc43504085ab8bacd6453fdd9189df7b55cc","tid":1301316,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2410568795705846/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F2410568795705846%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBDXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=f4753621\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2410568795705846/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66322243_2410568802372512_1667505002379214848_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQly_xdS9lXcLQOPzXrn4auaGnpRyZvHhSxsSdom0x2E1BOgakjZ1fR20fLVhvTULpE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=0300cbfd475be829f803041ecfd64467&amp;oe=5DABA1BB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66322243_2410568802372512_1667505002379214848_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQly_xdS9lXcLQOPzXrn4auaGnpRyZvHhSxsSdom0x2E1BOgakjZ1fR20fLVhvTULpE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D0300cbfd475be829f803041ecfd64467%26oe%3D5DABA1BB&h=c067fb38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近廣東省政府公布《粵港澳大灣區建設三年行動計劃（2018-2020年）》(註一)，除了全城關注的社會信用系統外，更有提及香港一條原本已「壽終正寢」的鐵路發展計劃&mdash;&mdash;港深西部快軌的復活大計。<br />\n<br />\n港府原本已在2014年宣佈直至2031年前都不擬興建港深西部快軌，因為快軌需要興建海底鐵路隧道，成本預計至少1,100億港元(2013年價格，相信今日的造價將更不菲)，整體財務可行性成疑(註二)。<br />\n<br />\n但今次《大灣區行動計劃》稱「與香港合作推動深港西部快速軌道的論證和規劃建設」，刻意重提本已難產的鐵路計劃，早前我們亦發現深圳市政府一直未有放棄，仍將港深西部快軌列入交通「十三五」規劃(詳見註三)，從多方面跡象可見，中國政府似乎想將快軌死而復生。<br />\n<br />\n難道一條原本預料會蝕本的大白象鐵路，只要放在「大灣區」的名目下就可以突然變得財政上可行? 港府稱一直與中央及粵澳政府保持緊密聯繫，共同制定及推出大灣區措施，不知道今次復活大計，港府到底是懵然不知地「被規劃」，抑或是與中國政府暗中合作，共同蒙騙香港市民?<br />\n<br />\n港深西部快軌除了吞噬公帑，更是配合大灣區「互聯互通」的區域融合，方便極速送中，民間必須齊上齊落，反對大白象基建。"},{"pid":"103a8a0595ae8642619bc33c1d94536e5cbc5ab0","tid":1301316,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"準備訓路軌啦"},{"pid":"15051777600ac6cc807cc18327e876cc013fda82","tid":1301316,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"48cbce933aee781abb95f7ff30b0b3a38672b3d7","tid":1301316,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2c603022126e9f708ba3a3b28927e0181802244","tid":1301316,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7aa5426fd377de925846ad68b21fc12a771d254","tid":1301316,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"光復上水7月13號<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dgzqDS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dgzqDS</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/09/232023_d71acc073516a1924d1df549cec7ee21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2F232023_d71acc073516a1924d1df549cec7ee21.jpg&h=8c9074d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29ecd08f87ba31cf82ec51359250711bb17d50e9","tid":1301316,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54336a14fac18a5d7870b654a5626812731cd61f","tid":1301316,"uid":117418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"好撚忙呀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"